  "@type": "SoftwareSourceCode",
  "identifier": "ggseg.meshes",
  "description": "Provides additional brain surface meshes for cortical and cerebellar visualisation in the 'ggseg' ecosystem. Cortical meshes include 'fsaverage5' pial, white, semi-inflated, sphere, smoothwm, and orig surfaces. Cerebellar meshes include the 'SUIT' flatmap surface. All meshes follow the same vertices/faces data frame format used by 'ggseg.formats' and 'ggseg3d'.",
  "name": "ggseg.meshes: Additional Brain Surface Meshes for the 'ggseg' Ecosystem",
